channel.title: [Delta] Error for spawning a shop?
channel.description:
[img]http://img695.imageshack.us/img695/3835/image01er.jpg[/img] I receive this error when [i]running[/i] my Delta source. Now, I've looked on tutorials and I'm pretty sure I have everything right, but here's what I have.
NPC: [code]if(NPCID == 545){ PutNPCCoords = true; WanneShop = 42; }[/code] Autospawn: [code]spawn = 545 3231 2913 0 0 0 0 0 1[/code] Shop: [code]shop = 42 Dragon_Weapons 1 1 1305 100 5698 100[/code]
Everything is correctly tabbed, I don't see what's happening! Thanks to anyone with any idea.
